{"tid":264454,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"請教過來人始何放下","createTime":"2017-05-30T23:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T07:41:05.000Z","uid":32976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f17fecf9682312d39969b5390af6e1232367bcd","tid":264454,"uid":32976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:21:04.000Z","msg":"家中小狗早兩日走了。<br />\n一起近十五年多一點。<br />\n<br />\n現在回家會很怕，亦想想唔開心同問自己係咪做得未夠好⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be266b5fbf298b98a53d3c3a0c2492a46dbc4ae","tid":264454,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:00:15.000Z","msg":"時間<br />\n<br />\n我用6年時間食藥忘記"},{"pid":"55567d2468b264198675974e5a36976a217a5659","tid":264454,"uid":1205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"時間<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗係2012年聖誕離開咗<br />\n嗰時無乜點喊 <br />\n因為無乜實感 唔覺得佢真係走咗<br />\n雖然佢條屍就喺我面前<br />\n<br />\n不過之後每年臨近聖誕都忍唔住諗返起<br />\n當日我一起身就見到佢攤喺路中心<br />\n其他狗都圍住佢<br />\n我想抱起佢 但佢個身好重好凍<br />\n<br />\n有時都會諗起佢啲毛嘅質感<br />\n我屋企有好幾隻狗 <br />\n每隻狗嘅毛嘅質地都唔同"},{"pid":"d83f6c43ef97f0b72130308eb1a0278836f2bddd","tid":264454,"uid":32976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"好難呢。原來生命中沒有，是十分之空虛⋯"},{"pid":"2ffdb153d79674d1215c8c6e1096885fee730e2f","tid":264454,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"去領養番隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78652b90de12b4c483f980bddb9a18326788046b","tid":264454,"uid":32976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去領養番隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會助養，暫養，但領養或再養就一定唔會了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de932be049d7c957cd0171f6452c76be8281fd22","tid":264454,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}